RecommendedActionErrorInfo RecommendedActionErrorInfo

Optional. Gets the estimated impact info for this recommended action E.g., Estimated CPU gain, Estimated Disk Space change

Value

Value
String String

Optional. Gets if approval for applying this recommended action is given by User/System.

Value
String String

Value
Nullable<System.DateTime> Nullable(Of System.DateTime)

ExecuteActionStartTime ExecuteActionStartTime

Optional. Gets the time when system started applying this recommended action on the user resource. E.g., Index creation start time

public System.DateTime? ExecuteActionStartTime { get; set; }Public Property ExecuteActionStartTime As System.DateTime?
Value
Nullable<System.DateTime> Nullable(Of System.DateTime)

Optional. Gets the implementation details of this recommended action for user to apply it manually.

Optional. Gets if this recommended action was already suggested some time ago but user chose to ignore this and System recommends again.

Value
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Edit

Optional. Gets if this recommended action is actionable to User

public bool ? IsExecutableAction { get; set; }Public Property IsExecutableAction As Boolean?
Value
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Edit

Optional. Gets if changes applied by this recommended action can be reverted by User

public bool ? IsRevertableAction { get; set; }Public Property IsRevertableAction As Boolean?
Value
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Value
DateTime DateTime

Value
IList<String> IList(Of String)

Optional. Gets the observed/actual impact info for this recommended action E.g., Actual CPU gain, Actual Disk Space change

Value
IList<RecommendedActionImpactInfo> IList(Of RecommendedActionImpactInfo)

RecommendationReason RecommendationReason

Edit

Optional. Gets the reason for recommending this action. E.g., DuplicateIndex

public string RecommendationReason { get; set; }Public Property RecommendationReason As String
Value
String String

RevertActionDuration RevertActionDuration

Edit

Optional. Gets the time taken for reverting changes of this recommended action on user resource. E.g., Time taken for dropping the created index.

public string RevertActionDuration { get; set; }Public Property RevertActionDuration As String
Value
String String

RevertActionInitiatedBy RevertActionInitiatedBy

Edit

Optional. Gets if approval for reverting this recommended action is given by User/System.

public string RevertActionInitiatedBy { get; set; }Public Property RevertActionInitiatedBy As String
Value
String String

RevertActionInitiatedTime RevertActionInitiatedTime

Edit

Optional. Gets the time when this recommended action is approved for revert

public System.DateTime? RevertActionInitiatedTime { get; set; }Public Property RevertActionInitiatedTime As System.DateTime?
Value
Nullable<System.DateTime> Nullable(Of System.DateTime)

RevertActionStartTime RevertActionStartTime

Edit

Optional. Gets the time when system started reverting changes of this recommended action on user resource. E.g., Time when Index drop is executed.

public System.DateTime? RevertActionStartTime { get; set; }Public Property RevertActionStartTime As System.DateTime?
Value
Nullable<System.DateTime> Nullable(Of System.DateTime)

Score Score

Edit

Optional. Gets the impact of this recommended actions. Possible values are 1 - Low impact, 2 - Medium Impact and 3 - High Impact

public int Score { get; set; }Public Property Score As Integer
Value
Int32 Int32

State State

Optional. Gets the info of the state the Recommended Action is in.

public RecommendedActionStateInfo State { get; set; }Public Property State As RecommendedActionStateInfo
Value
RecommendedActionStateInfo RecommendedActionStateInfo

TimeSeries TimeSeries

Optional. Gets the time series info of metrics for this recommended action E.g., CPU time series

public IList<RecommendedActionMetricInfo> TimeSeries { get; set; }Public Property TimeSeries As IList(Of RecommendedActionMetricInfo)
Value
IList<RecommendedActionMetricInfo> IList(Of RecommendedActionMetricInfo)

Optional. Gets the time since when this Recommended action is valid.

public DateTime ValidSince { get; set; }Public Property ValidSince As DateTime
